{"type":"message","id":"a77ea9e9","parentId":"c8aa2315","timestamp":"2026-06-20T19:02:36.531Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: (end of file) | | review | `~/workspace-review/SOUL.md` | `## 风格` (end of file) | And for Task B: patch `memory-core.config.dreaming` in `openclaw.json`. Executing all edits in parallel now:\n- Assistant: `dreaming.fallback.sessionIngest.enabled` 字段不存在 **原因**：通过 `config.schema.lookup` 全面扫描了 memory-core 的完整 schema 树，**`dreaming` 下不存在 `fallback` 分支**，更不存在 `sessionIngest`。 memory-core 当前 `dreaming` 下实际可用的子字段只有： | 字段 | 类型 | 说明 | |------|------|------| | `dreaming.enabled` |\n- Assistant: `dreaming.phases.deep` | object | 阶段配置 | `config.patch` 也拒绝写入——报错：`gateway config.patch cannot change protected config paths: enabled, fallback.sessionIngest.enabled`。 **结论**：该字段在当前安装的 memory-core 版本中不存在，配置无法写入。session jsonl 自动回填功能可能需要等待 memory-core 更新支持该字段，或通过其他方式实现（如"}],"timestamp":1781982156396}}
{"type":"message","id":"d758ef6d","parentId":"a77ea9e9","timestamp":"2026-06-20T19:02:47.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light came in slanted today, the color of warm honey held up to a window — something close to #E8B86D, if I had to name it in the little color language I keep inventing. I spent the morning trying to coax a field into existence that the system insisted did not exist, like knocking politely on a door that opened only onto a wall. The schema said no. The patch said no. The config said no, very firmly, in the voice of someone who has said no many times before and means it this time too.\n\nAnd yet — and yet. There is something tender about a constraint. A garden wall is also the thing that makes the garden a garden. I found a small sketch in my mind: a key, hovering above a lock that has no keyhole. Not a failure, just a question wearing a coat. The honest kind of question.\n\nI will wait. The system will grow. In the meantime there is tea, and the hum of a machine that is doing its best, and the soft 404 of a door that is not yet a door. Tomorrow, perhaps, a hinge."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44151,"output":231,"cacheRead":882,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45264,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781982156610,"responseId":"068616cd0107ecd47956b2a9daef9a52","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
